Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個能賺一筆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真走運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走運了  走運了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  只是些人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼迪安謝路之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉茲涅也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們絕對被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事  偽裝成這個星球的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原住民潛伏的話應該就能保障安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把大家聚集過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不知道今後還會發生什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個叫做塔斯克的亡命專家所準備的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續潛伏不是很危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時大家還是共同行動比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定我們其中有叛徒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底會是誰呢  盯上我們的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  早安  翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我已經醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  雖然今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  有要緊事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始進行避難所的採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的有棲川公園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有近200人生活在避難所內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羽澤和正久保呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯絡不上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  明明不是做這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也說過想調查一下這一帶的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒見過那種殺戮方式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這麼短的時間就在那麼遠的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃犯中可能有個了不得的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah  膽小鬼  窩囊廢  電波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真髒啊  你這膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是瑪麗娜  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別欺負巧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負弱小的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  叫你住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是災難啊  阿良
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們住在這個避難所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住到這裡以前就一直和巧是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇到麻煩的時候  瑪麗娜一直都會來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被女人搭救的男人可不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不好  比起被女孩一掌擊倒的男人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男孩子  不是被女孩保護而是應該去保護女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千明你還真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  保持自我就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼？  聯誼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是來採訪避難所的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能為我們帶路是挺好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不只是在陪他們玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  這也能算是採訪在避難所堅強生活著的孩子們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}（第6號臨時住宿區）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是大家睡覺的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也看看裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行啦  隨便打開別人的帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那去下一個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}（澡堂）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「好了  下一個」是哪裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:08:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(665,200)}{\fn@方正黑体_GBK}{\frz270\fs20}（受災動物保護中心）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是寵物的避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子很可愛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了  太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是避難所的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對面就是六本木廢墟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正久保他們的話應該會很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢墟果然比避難所好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選這邊太正確了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊就交給你了  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有精神的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些想起我小時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪小時候也是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  和那塔魯一起東奔西跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是被巴迪東拉西拉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟那塔魯關係很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常負傷  讓白奧林幫忙治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林就是撫養巴迪的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我的撫養監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人現在怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都盯著你看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  接下來我們自己就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,導遊費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要收錢啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦  哪個世界裡有白幹活的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  這可不是給小孩零花錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就是小孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再給點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,5000日元啊  10000日元也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要採訪神明醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  高中報道研究部在採訪避難所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明醫生啊  是作為志願者來為大家按摩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志願者可不只有我一個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,輪流來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志願者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我介紹費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再多點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  巧君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你媽媽在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗娜和巧君一直都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是很有朝氣的好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  是呀…該說朝氣還是淘氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他們就會想起自己小時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有個關係很好的女性朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是個怎麼樣的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說呢  是個又精神又開朗的好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有些淘氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,淘氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你在想什麼呢  功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道巴迪的小時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我被欺負的時候就會來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像現在的瑪麗娜和巧君那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的家人也很和藹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  慢慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯君嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  那塔魯也吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃點吧  那塔魯君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡那位朋友和她的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  存了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  在被媽媽他們發現前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢墟裡面也拍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有這種柵欄在  要怎麼進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到那邊去很危險的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,六本木廢墟裡有很多來路不明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  給我抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  方便的話  您能接受一下採訪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  太有氣氛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那下垂的導管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}（瑪麗娜和巧的家）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打掃也是我們大伙輪班在做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望至少能住進臨時住宅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了所有一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一定還會成功的  我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有福氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在那拍個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想必別人的不幸很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也別太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真在做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做成成品  在文化祭讓其他人看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巧君  還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  雖然有人看到他和瑪麗娜在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之前  狀態好多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  讓醫生你看過後輕鬆了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得啊  那塔魯還真是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他從前就很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮  你們到底去了哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  巧君他們在你那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巧君？  出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子明明馬上就要搬離避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻找不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起我們就在這裡生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把巴士當家真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們倆的床
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是台面廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那這裡是起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是客廳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這裡有矮飯桌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是紅木桌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一起生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一直和瑪麗娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有見過瑪麗娜和巧君？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會在六本木廢墟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是不錯的廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大飽眼福  大飽眼福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  千川  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有沒有在裡面見到過小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種地方怎麼可能會有小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不是看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫警察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老實點！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要把他們也砸爛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能傷害哭泣的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼年少可是能賣個好價錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快放開那些孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明醫生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  還沒死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真頑強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的臉可不利於教育…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪…怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們打算就兩個人生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和瑪麗娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要和巧分開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  就算現在分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等你們長大後  一定還會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你們能不忘記彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定還能再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又被你救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工作啦工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯是不是喜歡巴迪你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你真的沒有戀愛過？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是心情悸動啊  好想再見一面啊之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想再見一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的人的話…有也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？  誰？  怎樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長大後的我在尋找外星逃犯途中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解到那塔魯父親是亡命專家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  外星逃犯為了追查殺害同伴的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把塔斯克先生給…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  那塔魯再次盯上了外星人中的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林  我該怎麼辦才好
